    <item>
      <title>拉里·霍根 (Larry Hogan) 从倡导小组辞职，引发有关 2024 年申办的讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/larry-hogan-steps-down-from-no-labels-fueling-talk-of-2024-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，温和派共和党人、前马里兰州州长拉里·霍根 (Larry Hogan) 辞去了中间派倡导组织“无标签”(No Labels) 全国名誉联合主席的职务。此举可能会加剧有关他通过第三方竞选总统的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/larry-hogan-steps-down-from-no-labels-fueling-talk-of-2024-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登对加州税收指控不认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/hunter-biden-pleads-not-guilty-to-us-tax-charges-in-california</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登对联邦指控表示无罪，指控他未能对来自外国企业的数百万美元收入缴税，共和党人希望这一案件能够支持对他父亲、总统乔·拜登的弹劾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/hunter-biden-pleads-not-guilty-to-us-tax-charges-in-california</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称历史表明特朗普获胜将构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/lagarde-says-history-suggests-a-trump-victory-would-be-a-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德警告称，回顾唐纳德·特朗普作为美国总统的第一个任期，人们会担心他可能在 2025 年重新掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/lagarde-says-history-suggests-a-trump-victory-would-be-a-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国总理与央行的冲突升级令投资者担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/thai-pm-s-escalating-clash-with-central-bank-on-rate-cuts-worries-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理正在发起十年来最大规模的降息运动，加剧与央行的政策冲突，这可能会损害投资者对亚洲表现最差市场之一的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/thai-pm-s-escalating-clash-with-central-bank-on-rate-cuts-worries-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国反倾销调查给欧洲干邑生产商带来重重痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-anti-dumping-probe-piles-pain-on-europe-s-cognac-producers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京最近与欧盟的贸易紧张局势不断加剧，加剧了当地干邑经销商在中国经济放缓期间难以转移库存的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-anti-dumping-probe-piles-pain-on-europe-s-cognac-producers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙继续让勒梅尔担任财务主管，这是连续性的标志</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/french-government-reshuffle-macron-keeps-le-maire-as-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 选择保持经济政策的连续性，在改组后的政府中重新任命布鲁诺·勒梅尔 (Bruno Le Maire) 为财政部长，延长了自 2017 年就任总统以来推动亲商改革议程的密切伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/french-government-reshuffle-macron-keeps-le-maire-as-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 18:48:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁审查预计将持续一年或更长时间，与预测相悖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/biden-review-of-us-steel-deal-seen-dragging-on-maybe-into-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国对新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的国家安全审查不太可能在今年年底结束，并且可能会延长至 2025 年，时间远远长于这些公司公开表示的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/biden-review-of-us-steel-deal-seen-dragging-on-maybe-into-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 18:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
