    <item>
      <title>审判结束后，特朗普告诉纽约法官，对他的指控是“欺诈”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/trump-fraud-trial-based-on-political-agenda-lawyer-tells-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，唐纳德·特朗普在法庭上出人意料地发表了结案陈词，猛烈抨击纽约州对他进行的为期三个月的欺诈审判，但被法官阿瑟·恩戈伦打断，因为这位前总统声称此案是政治迫害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/trump-fraud-trial-based-on-political-agenda-lawyer-tells-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装领导人誓言将对美国的任何军事袭击做出“重大”回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/houthi-leader-vows-big-response-to-any-us-military-assault</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装领导人威胁称，如果美国及其盟友对其采取军事行动，他们将做出“重大”回应。该组织近两个月来一直在红海袭击船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/houthi-leader-vows-big-response-to-any-us-military-assault</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
